172 A.3d 1083 NEW JERSEY STATE POLICE, PETITIONER-RESPONDENT, v. TROOPER NICOLE CUSANELLI #6166, RESPONDENT-PETITIONER.

C-263 September Term 2017

079152 November 9, 2017

ON PETITION FOR CERTIFICATION

To the Appellate Division, Superior Court:

A petition for certification of the judgment in A-005611-14 having been submitted to this Court, and the Court having considered the same;

It is ORDERED that the petition for certification is denied, with costs.
